10#include <isl_multi_macro.h>
11
12/* Does "multi" involve any NaNs?
13 */
14isl_bool FN(MULTI(BASE),involves_nan)(__isl_keep MULTI(BASE) *multi)
15{
16 return FN(MULTI(BASE),any)(multi, &FN(EL,involves_nan));
17}
